# Project Meta
- Unity 6.0.3f1, URP, NGO, New Input System.
- UI stack: UI Toolkit first, with data binding preferred whenever practical.
- C# 12; async uses `Awaitable`.
- `Assets/Design/` (GDD/NDD) is the design source of truth.

## Organization
- Assets split by `Systems/` (reusable), `Features/` (project), `Core/` (shared glue).
- Enforce boundaries with per-system `.asmdef`.
- Use `--- SECTION ---` hierarchy separators in scenes.
